page_description: Learn about the different model capabilities that are available with Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: GPT-4GPT-4 is the predecessor to GPT-4 Turbo. Both the GPT-4 and GPT-4 Turbo models have a base model name of `gpt-4`. You can distinguish between the GPT-4 and Turbo models by examining the model version.- `gpt-4` Version `0314`- `gpt-4` Version `0613`- `gpt-4-32k` Version `0613`You can see the token context length supported by each model in the model summary table.
